content: Convenient analyzing of the collected responses

comment.text: This translation key describes a header used in a dialog that provides analyzing capabilities of collected responses. The header is intended to be displayed as part of a form-filling tips dialog, guiding users on how to analyze their responses.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The English phrase 'Convenient analyzing of the collected responses' implies ease and efficiency in analyzing the responses. While 'تحليل مريح للإجابات المجمعة' translates to 'Comfortable analysis of the collected responses', 'مريح' (comfortable) doesn't fully capture the intended meaning of 'convenient' in this context. 'سهل' (easy) or 'يسير' (straightforward/simple) would be more accurate alternatives.

The translation 'Kätevä kerättyjen vastausten analysointi' is a literal translation and doesn't convey the same meaning as 'Convenient analyzing of the collected responses'. It sounds slightly awkward in Finnish. 'Kerättyjen vastausten analysointi' is a bit too technical and formal for a dialog header offering a tip.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: A better translation would be something like 'Helppo analysoida kerättyjä vastauksia' or 'Helppoa analysoida vastauksia'.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The English phrase 'Convenient analyzing' is better translated as 'Analyse aisée' or 'Analyse facile' to convey the same meaning of ease or simplicity. 'Pratique' implies practicality or usefulness, which is a slightly different nuance.

The English phrase 'Convenient analyzing' implies ease and efficiency. 'Pratica' in Italian, while meaning practical, doesn't fully capture the 'convenient' aspect. A better translation might emphasize ease or simplicity.
The translation '수집된 응답 간단 분석' is too literal and doesn't convey the nuance of 'Convenient analyzing of the collected responses.' It lacks the implication of ease or benefit.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: 수집된 응답의 간편 분석 (Suejp-doen ungeop-ui ganpyeon bunseok)

ai_spell_check_issues.description: While grammatically correct, the sentence structure feels somewhat abrupt in Korean. Adding a particle or restructuring could improve flow.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: 수집된 응답을 간편하게 분석 (Suejp-doen ungeop-eul ganpyeonhage bunseok)

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The Lao translation "ການວິເຄາະຜົນການຕອບສະແດງທີ່ເຕົ້າໂຮມໄວ້ຢ່າງສະດວກສະບາຍ" is a literal translation and doesn't quite capture the nuance of 'Convenient analyzing of the collected responses'. It sounds a bit clunky and formal. A more natural translation might emphasize the ease and efficiency of the analysis.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Consider a translation like "ການວິເຄາະຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ເຕົ້າໂຮມໄວ້ ງ່າຍດາຍ ແລະ ມີປະສິດທິພາບ" (Easy and efficient analysis of collected data) or "ວິເຄາະຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ເຕົ້າໂຮມໄວ້ຢ່າງສະຫງ່າງາມ" (Elegant analysis of collected data).

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The English phrase 'Convenient analyzing' is better translated as 'Análise facilitada' or 'Análise simples' rather than 'Análise cómoda'. 'Cómoda' implies comfortable, which isn't the intended meaning in this context.

The translation 'එකතු කරන ලද ප්‍රතිචාර විශ්ලේෂණය කිරීම පහසුයි.' while conveying a similar meaning, isn't the most natural or precise translation of 'Convenient analyzing of the collected responses'. A more accurate translation would emphasize the convenience aspect more directly.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: ගබර ලද ප්‍රතිචාර විශ්ලේෂණය කිරීමේ පහසුව.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The Serbian translation "Лако анализирање прикупљених одговора" doesn't fully capture the meaning of "Convenient analyzing of the collected responses." 'Лако' translates to 'easily' or 'lightly,' which doesn't convey the 'convenient' aspect. A more accurate translation would emphasize convenience or ease of use.
The translation 'Lako analiziranje prikupljenih odgovora' doesn't fully capture the nuance of 'Convenient analyzing of the collected responses'. 'Lako' implies 'easy' rather than 'convenient'.

The translation 'Phân tích thuận tiện các câu trả lời thu thập được' is somewhat literal and doesn't fully capture the nuance of 'Convenient analyzing of the collected responses'. It sounds a bit clunky in Vietnamese.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Phân tích dễ dàng các câu trả lời đã thu thập

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation '方便分析收集到的回答' doesn't fully capture the nuance of 'Convenient analyzing of the collected responses'. While '方便分析' means 'convenient analysis', the phrasing is a bit clunky.  'Analyzing' implies a process or capability, and '方便' only addresses the ease of the analysis.  It misses the 'convenient' aspect of the whole process.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: 可便捷地分析收集到的回答
